Upstream-Name: seafile-server
Source: https://github.com/haiwen/seafile-server
Comment:
 This source package pulls in several upstream repositories by tag as additional
 components, each unpacked into its own directory: libsearpc/, libevhtp/,
 seahub/, seafobj/, seafdav/ and seafevents/ (all from https://github.com/haiwen).

